title: Windows Applications 0-Days [R-Z] - November - Ongoing
description:
These are scene Releases and 0 day applications
To Extract
First select all the zip files by dragging your mouse over them. Then unzip them to a different folder. At the new folder you will find a set of rars .Do the exact same procedure as the zips but this time select the extract here option. That should do it. It's safe to delete the rars now. If you are having trouble with the extraction of the rars upgrade your winrar to version 5.
